Title: lnx_if: Use MAC address from command 'ip' if the command 'ethtool' is not available
Level: 1
Component: inv
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.5.0p24
Date: 1573120800
Class: fix

If 'ethtool' is not installed or not available then the HW/SW inventory
does not inventorize MAC addresses of interfaces.
In above case we use 'link/ether' from command 'ip'.
